reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Good and Easy Assembly
reviews.reviewText: Very happy with this purchase! I was worried about how good it would be and I’m impressed!! It’s very nice, made well and came with perfect assembly instructions and easy to put together. It was packed very well in the box with no damages and the pieces to put it together were packaged and labeled nicely, it even included a Phillips head screwdriver. All the holes were lined up perfectly on the wood pieces to fit the screws and pegs in. ⭐️Just a quick note: the instruction booklet was in a spot that you can miss and throw out by mistake with packing materials, so carefully go through the box after you take out the furniture and assembly pieces to find the instructions booklet. I highly recommend this!! I’m so happy I took the chance and ordered it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I was a little skeptical about purchasing this buffet cabinet because it didn't have many reviews. I'm glad I decided to buy it. The instructions were good and it was easy to assemble. The parts include a Phillips screwdriver however I decided to use my drill especially for assembling the back panel. The instructions stated "team assembly recommended" but I put it together by myself with no problems. It matches my floors perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Product arrived on time, price was reasonable, directions were very clear and parts were all labeled. I put it together in about an hour. Negative - There was tape on the back of the and when I started to pull it off it peeled the backing. I just left the tape, not a big deal as no one sees the back anyway. Besides that the price was good, it's not real wood, however, if it were it would of costs much more. I did order another one as the storage area is quite large and held my sewing items very well. Out of sight out of mind.
